adjustments to it, so it fits better.

57:22.473 --> 57:24.943
It's custom made. There's only one
like it in the whole wide world.

57:25.043 --> 57:28.479
- I love it! Yeah?
- You love it? Yeah? Oh, good.

57:29.472 --> 57:31.315
Just congratulations.

57:33.249 --> 57:35.104
Are you happy?

57:36.527 --> 57:40.720
Good. We gotta get that money
so I can afford to pay off that ring.

57:43.960 --> 57:47.397
Why don't you go take care of her
and I'll go find that cash?

57:48.531 --> 57:50.334
I love you.

57:52.502 --> 57:54.328
