58:17.927 --> 58:20.164
This is so fucking ninja.

58:26.102 --> 58:29.306
<i>10-18, can I get a status check
on Crescent Place?</i>

58:42.018 --> 58:43.888
Code 6, standby.

58:43.988 --> 58:45.789
