01:01:03.198 --> 01:01:05.129
You sneaky son of a bitch.

01:01:05.229 --> 01:01:08.972
- Never would have guessed.
- Well, I'm just full of surprises.

01:01:29.252 --> 01:01:32.456
Hey, my music isn't
