01:05:01.564 --> 01:05:03.566
Come on, give it to me.

01:05:04.166 --> 01:05:07.304
- You shot my arm.
- Give it to me!

01:05:07.404 --> 01:05:08.938
Jesus!

01:05:09.706 --> 01:05:14.211
You know, this is a $500 jacket, man!
I'm still making payments on it.

01:05:14.311 --> 01:05:18.379
Give it to me. Come on, come on.

01:05:46.909 --> 01:05:50.680
- What the fuck happened to you?
- He ran around to the front of the house.

01:05:50.780 --> 01:05:52.713
Go cut him off.

01:05:52.813 --> 01:05:57.387
Okay, cool. Anyways, this guy...
