01:06:31.921 --> 01:06:33.924
Hi, Patrick!

01:06:35.958 --> 01:06:37.961
Hi-ya, Alex!

01:06:38.861 --> 01:06:40.865
What happened here?

01:06:41.665 --> 01:06:45.503
