01:08:07.183 --> 01:08:09.452
Screw you, Patrick.

01:08:11.687 --> 01:08:14.838
I'm running a little bit low on time.

01:08:37.779 --> 01:08:39.582
Hey, Clarence!

01:08:40.916 --> 01:08:42.752
Where you at, white boy?

01:08:47.622 --> 01:08:49.438
I'm gonna get you.

01:08:51.227 --> 01:08:53.096
Come on.

01:08:53.596 --> 01:08:56.033
Don't you know ninjas can see in the dark?

01:09:15.385 --> 01:09:17.187
