01:12:09.392 --> 01:12:11.394
Let's go, we can't stay here, let's go!

01:12:16.899 --> 01:12:19.574
I got you mother-truckers now.

01:12:35.183 --> 01:12:38.822
Clarence?
You're literally killing me right now.

01:12:39.522 --> 01:12:41.859
<i>Political activist Emma Goldman once said...</i>

01:12:41.959 --> 01:12:45.771
<i>"The most violent element
in society is ignorance."</i>

01:12:51.234 --> 01:12:52.836
Shit!

01:13:22.097 --> 01:13:23.900
I didn't think you'd still be here!

01:13:24.000 --> 01:13:26.670
Yeah, well I had some unfinished business!

01:13:33.041 --> 01:13:36.346
