cops are on their way!

01:13:36.446 --> 01:13:38.249
Yeah, I know!

01:13:39.249 --> 01:13:43.177
Say, you're not just some
rich kid with a crush, are ya?

01:13:46.689 --> 01:13:48.258
Nope.

01:13:49.058 --> 01:13:51.364
