01:13:51.464 --> 01:13:53.096
Yep.

01:13:54.830 --> 01:13:58.034
Say, where'd you get the money
that you gave me to begin with?

01:13:58.134 --> 01:14:00.970
My grandmother actually gave me
a little money when she died.

01:14:02.489 --> 01:14:04.942
You're not a Duffield, are you?

01:14:05.742 --> 01:14:07.278
Nope.

01:14:08.278 --> 01:14:11.214
Yeah, piece of shit car
in the garage gave you away.

01:14:11.314 --> 01:14:14.509
- What happened to the nice one?
- It was a rental.

01:14:14.609 --> 01:14:16.485
And the house?

01:14:19.054 --> 01:14:21.558
Craigslist, vacation rental section.

01:14:21.658 --> 01:14:23.900
Couple grand for a few nights.

01:14:25.027 --> 01:14:26.831
Not a bad deal.

01:14:27.681 --> 01:14:30.029
Not gonna get your deposit back, though.

01:14:32.791 --> 01:14:34.320
Shit.

01:14:36.527 --> 01:14:39.341
Sounds like you're all
out of bargaining chips.

01:14:43.479 --> 01:14:45.882
Hey, Alex, you wanna hear a secret?

01:14:54.923 --> 01:14:58.484
Looks like we got ourselves
a little Mexican standoff here.

01:15:04.599 --> 01:15:06.690
Minus the Mexican.

01:15:08.674 --> 01:15:12.542
Didn't anyone ever tell you not to bring
a knife to a gunfight, Clarence?

01:15:15.644 --> 01:15:18.948
Say, baby cakes,
what if I told you that Clarence here...

01:15:19.048 --> 01:15:22.162
...had this whole night
planned out from the get go?

01:15:23.352 --> 01:15:26.788
He did. It's true.

01:15:27.923 --> 01:15:29.738
